column5: Of course OFC has to be #1 in all our books   but im getting bored with the other sites that i visit routinely. What are you guys killing your time with on the web?
A couple of our local news sites, our local fishing board, MNR fire site recently(frequently), for obvious reasons, weather sites, a couple other non fishing sites, but mostly, OFC.
been playing this http://www.andkon.com/arcade/missiledefender/vrdefendery3k/ all day  pretty addictive
OFC, Tackletour.com, The weather network, japan tackle web-sites.  I Also game from time to time Battlefield 2142 and Northern Strike, Counterstrike Source, Ghost Recon Advanced Warfighter.
mostly here and hockeydraft.ca, nhl.com and the internet crack that is facebook!
hm.. this site.. a few classfieds, ebay to check out any deals.. that'd be about it...
